name: Rebirth (itch) (Drather2303, MalvogHekopt)
description:
We are sorry...

It was supposed to have reincarnation in the end of a level so you can start the level again in a body of a new creature, but we did not have time... 

It was also supposed to have spikes, tramplesnes and other stuff, but well, now we have a worm...

Aghhhh... so we fucked something up and the menu does not load the level in the build... if someone knows why this might be, your help is much appreciated
